summary: This is an email from the NYSReportServer at the DOJ distributing the 'Child Exploitation & Porn Update Report III' for Project Safe Childhood. It instructs Chiefs and the Project Safe Childhood Coordinator to remind assigned AUSAs to update their cases.
keyFacts: The email is from the NYSReportServer at the DOJ (usa.doj.gov) and is dated February 23, 2021.
The subject is 'Child Exploitation & Porn Update Report III' and it is related to Project Safe Childhood.
The email instructs 'Chiefs and Project Safe Childhood Coordinator' to remind assigned Assistant U.S. Attorneys (AUSAs) to update their cases.
The document identifier is EFTA00096770, which is part of Data Set 9 in the released documents.
The email serves as a distribution mechanism for an internal DOJ report on child exploitation cases.
